830
01:03:47,407 --> 01:03:49,492
And if you die?

831
01:03:50,535 --> 01:03:52,578
Then will the price be high enough?

832
01:03:55,123 --> 01:03:57,583
-l have no choice.
-Why?

833
01:03:59,711 --> 01:04:01,587
He is your father too.

834
01:04:11,431 --> 01:04:14,266
l finally understand it now, Trix.

835
01:04:14,434 --> 01:04:16,560
l know why he left us.

836
01:04:17,646 --> 01:04:22,233
He was trying to change this rotten
business and they killed him for it.

837
01:04:35,205 --> 01:04:38,374
A lot of drivers beIieve that
the hardest part of Cristo is the start.

838
01:04:38,542 --> 01:04:41,085
The Muqranna?
