879
01:10:50,955 --> 01:10:52,581
Flying in.

880
01:10:55,335 --> 01:10:57,502
-Lead them.
-Here you go.

881
01:10:59,005 --> 01:11:00,005
Ha-ha!

882
01:11:18,191 --> 01:11:19,900
Watch the blind side!

883
01:11:28,910 --> 01:11:31,620
Broom Hilda!

884
01:11:34,290 --> 01:11:38,377
Crom!

